title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Agent
description:
The Agent is the ultimate alley slasher, with a unique shape that features deep concave, functional kicktails, and cutouts that offer your feet reference points and added control.
Artist: Eric Waetzig

L: 35.00” W: 9.50” WB: 20.00”
To learn more about the Agent visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/agent/
